@HCL_Food_Delivery_HostAddress = https://localhost:5001
@token = REPLACE_WITH_JWT
@userId = 1
@orderId = 1

### Login
POST {{HCL_Food_Delivery_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@food.local",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

### Categories
GET {{HCL_Food_Delivery_HostAddress}}/api/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### Foods
GET {{HCL_Food_Delivery_HostAddress}}/api/foods?categoryId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### Create Order
POST {{HCL_Food_Delivery_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": {{userId}},
  "items": [
    { "foodItemId": 1, "quantity": 2, "price": 0 }
  ],
  "totalAmount": 0
}

### User Order History
GET {{HCL_Food_Delivery_HostAddress}}/api/orders/user/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### Update Order Status (admin)
PUT {{HCL_Food_Delivery_HostAddress}}/api/orders/{{orderId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

"Preparing"
